ers phe products are used in various industries such as hvac refrigeration electric power generation  distribution petroleum refinement chemical processing metallurgy and food  beverages to increase energy capture reduce operating costs and maintain stable temperatures as required during the production process for more information on product applications and advantages click below plate heat exchanger phes are used in a wide variety of industries but most commonly utilized in petroleum refinement power generation food  beverage processing and chemical processing phes are constructed through the use of specifically manufactured stainless steel and metal alloys heat transfer plates welded together and are often referred to as the phe within phe units and networks click here for more information     compact phe unit phe units are used in petroleum refinement power generation and related hvac distribution food  beverage processing and chemical processing industries while smartheats phe units are click here for more information     heat meters while heating companies in many european and nordic countries have long used meters to measure how much heat is used to warm buildings click here for more information   copyright  smartheat inc        smartheat newsrelease   smartheat announces appointment of chief financial officer audit committee chairman july  smartheat inc announces first quarter  financial results may  smartheat inc announces financial results for  april  smartheat q  financials november  smartheat inc announces third quarter  financial results is well positioned for future investor conference call at  am est on november   november  smartheat inc to report second quarter  financial results on august   before us market opens august  smartheat inc to report first quarter  financial results on may   before us market opens may  smartheat inc announces record full year  financial results   revenue growth  net income growth march  smartheat inc acquires german heat 