ider of phe products to chinas petroleum refining chemicals and petrochemicals energy generation steel medical electronics food and beverage processing manufacturing sectors and residential markets the phe units reduce energy wastage regulate heat transfer and pressure drop and maintain even the distribution of heating and cooling systems smartheat inc markets its products through its sales force and national distributors and sells phes under the sondex brand and phe units designed by its engineers and assembled with sondex plates under taiyu brand name the company is playing a significant role in helping china to manage pollution and improve its energy efficiency